title: Enigma - Union Square
description: A health food store chain location in the city center is the largest store with the biggest selection of foods. Offers supplements and herbs, teas, cereals, nuts and seeds, condiments, rice, cooking oils, sweets and snacks, vegan products (tofu, vegetable milks, soy yogurts, vegan spreads)  and many more. If you live in the city ask for the free membership card that gives you a 5% discount.
